FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]

) AS [t]

    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]

) AS [t]

    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]

LEFT JOIN (

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[madon] = @__donHangId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]

    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong]

) AS [t]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]

    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

) AS [t]

    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

2024-12-23 20:36:14.651 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (77ms) [Parameters=[@__userId_0='?' (Size = 450)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]

2024-12-23 20:36:43.838 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (81ms) [Parameters=[@__userId_0='?' (Size = 450)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]

    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]

    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

) AS [t]

    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]

    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]

) AS [t]

    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]

2024-12-23 21:51:07.294 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (232ms) [Parameters=[@__userId_0='?' (Size = 450)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]

    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]

    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

) AS [t]

    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]

SELECT [t].[madon], [t].[gia], [t].[giaohang], [t].[makh], [t].[ngaydat], [t].[ngaygiao], [t].[thanhtoan], [t].[tinhtrang], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop], [t0].[dongia], [t0].[soluong], [t0].[malaptop0], [t0].[cpu], [t0].[giaban], [t0].[gpu], [t0].[hardware], [t0].[hinh], [t0].[mahang], [t0].[manhinh], [t0].[manhucau], [t0].[mota], [t0].[ngaycapnhat], [t0].[pin], [t0].[ram], [t0].[soluongton], [t0].[tenlaptop], [t0].[trangthai]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]
    FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[madon] = [t0].[madon]
ORDER BY [t].[madon], [t0].[madon], [t0].[malaptop]
